@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Admin Sign Up

actor Admin
participant "Frontend/UI" as UI
participant "Backend/API" as API
participant "Validation Layer" as VAL
database "Database (Neon)" as DB
participant "Email Service (Optional)" as MAIL

Admin -> UI: Open 'Create Admin Account' page

Admin -> UI: Fill form + Submit
UI -> UI: Client-side validation
UI -> API: POST /trl/admin (Admin data)

API -> VAL: Validate payload schema
VAL --> API: Valid / Invalid

alt Invalid Data
    API --> UI: 400 Validation Error
    UI --> Admin: Show validation error
else Valid
    API -> DB: Check email already exists
    alt Email Exists
        API --> UI: 409 Conflict (Email already used)
        UI --> Admin: Show duplicate email error
    else Email Not Exists
        API -> API: Hash password (bcrypt/argon2)
        API -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
        API -> DB: Insert new admin record
        DB --> API: Insert success
        API -> DB: COMMIT

        opt Email Verification
            API -> MAIL: Send verification email
            MAIL --> API: Sent
        end

        API --> UI: 201 Created
        UI --> Admin: Show success message
        UI -> UI: Redirect to Admin homepage
    end
end



@enduml